  "clauseContent": "1.2.3.3.  公益性生物资产常见业务\n<div class=\"quill-better-table-wrapper\"><table class=\"quill-better-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><colgroup><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"><col width=\"auto\"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-row=\"1\"><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">业务场景</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">会计分录&nbsp;(执行企业会计准则)</strong></p></td><td data-row=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(245, 247, 250);\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line ql-align-center\" data-row=\"1\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\" data-cell-bg=\"rgb(245, 247, 250)\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">说明</strong></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"2\"><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（1）外购树苗或自行营造</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借：公益性生物资产</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">贷：银行存款</span></p></td><td data-row=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"2\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">达到预定生产经营目的前</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"3\"><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（2）天然起源的公益性生物资产</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借：&nbsp;公益性生物资产</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">贷：营业外收入</span></p></td><td data-row=\"3\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"3\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">按名义金额</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"4\"><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（3）消耗性生物资产、生产性生物资产转为公益性生物资产</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借：公益性生物资产</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;生产性生物资产累计折旧</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;生产性生物资产减值准备</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;存货跌价准备</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">贷：消耗性生物资产、生产性生物资产</span></p></td><td data-row=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"4\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">——</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"5\"><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（4）择伐、间伐或抚育更新等生产性采伐而补植林木类公益性生物资产发生的后续支出</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借：消耗性生物资产</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">贷：银行存款</span></p></td><td data-row=\"5\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"5\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">——</span></p></td></tr><tr data-row=\"6\"><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"1\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">（5）林木类公益性生物资产郁闭后发生的管护费用等其他后续支出</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">借：管理费用</span></p><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"2\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">贷：银行存款</span></p></td><td data-row=\"6\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\"><p class=\"qlbt-cell-line\" data-row=\"6\" data-cell=\"3\" data-rowspan=\"1\" data-colspan=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">——</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
